text: Jacques Déprez (3 March 1938 – 20 November 2020) was a French hurdler. He competed in the men's 110 metres hurdles at the 1960 Summer Olympics. Déprez died on 20 November 2020 at the age of 82.Jacky Desprez est mort ==References== Category:1938 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Olympians for France Category:French hurdlers
